                <td bgcolor="#e9e9e9" valign="top"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;07/28/2003&nbsp;: 1:47:46 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> It really wasnt a slam, and im sorry for making it seem that way, but its important that you learn sooner then later. The mobs only get faster, and hit harder the further you progress in levels.<br />Here are a few things to remember.<br />Re-apply darkness on the 131 tick of splurt. <br />LvL 4 fear is the ultimate aggro.<br />Wait for a tick of any dot, run awhile and sit back down before the next tick goes off. Make sure you are always sitting for the next tick. Humm something to help you out with timing, and it will be second nature for you. <br />With and doubt pull to a wall, even in PoP mobs dont wander there (well not often at least)<br /></span></font></td>
